The paper deals with different epistemic notions and their corresponding logics, as well as their dynamics. This suggests that it could belong to the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses awareness and knowledge, which are topics commonly studied in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The study of bisimulation is also relevant to Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper's focus on modal logic and axiomatizations could also place it in the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG).
